<div class="athlete-categories-section page-width">
  <div class="athlete-categories-grid">

    <div class="athlete-category-card">
      <div class="athlete-category-card__header athlete-category-card__header--juniors">
        <span class="athlete-category-card__label">Maximum Juniors</span>
        <span class="athlete-category-card__age">Ages 12–18</span>
      </div>
      <div class="athlete-category-card__body">
        <p>Our junior program develops athletes from the ground up — technique, strength, and confidence across all track and field disciplines.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Open to athletes aged <strong>12 and over</strong></li>
          <li>Athletes aged <strong>10–11</strong> considered under coach consultation based on squad size, training ability, and experience</li>
          <li>Program transitions to Opens at age 19</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="athlete-category-card__note">Not sure if your child is ready? Register for a free Come &amp; Try and our coaches will assess on the day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="athlete-category-card">
      <div class="athlete-category-card__header athlete-category-card__header--opens">
        <span class="athlete-category-card__label">Opens</span>
        <span class="athlete-category-card__age">Ages 19–30</span>
      </div>
      <div class="athlete-category-card__body">
        <p>For athletes competing or looking to compete at open level. Training is structured around performance outcomes and competition preparation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Athletes aged <strong>19 to 30</strong></li>
          <li>Athletes of any age competing in <strong>Athletics Australia</strong> or <strong>Athletics NSW Open</strong> events</li>
          <li>All disciplines — sprints, hurdles, jumps, throws, gym-based conditioning</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="athlete-category-card__note">Currently competing at open level over 30? You qualify for Opens.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="athlete-category-card">
      <div class="athlete-category-card__header athlete-category-card__header--masters">
        <span class="athlete-category-card__label">Masters</span>
        <span class="athlete-category-card__age">Ages 30+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="athlete-category-card__body">
        <p>Masters athletics is one of the most competitive and rewarding categories in the sport. Our coaches understand the demands of masters competition and periodise accordingly.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>30 and over</strong> for Australian competition</li>
          <li><strong>35 and over</strong> for World Masters Athletics international competition</li>
          <li>Training load monitored across micro and macro cycles to manage recovery</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="athlete-category-card__note">Ashley McMahon ran sub-11 seconds for 16 consecutive years from age 29–45. We understand masters performance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .athlete-categories-section {
    padding: 48px 20px 32px;
  }

  .athlete-categories-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .athlete-categories-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .athlete-category-card {
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__header {
    padding: 24px 20px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__header--juniors {
    background-color: #82f2b3;
    color: #0a2910;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__header--opens {
    background-color: #27282a;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__header--masters {
    background-color: #4661cb;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__label {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__age {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__body {
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__body p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__body ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__body li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #444;
  }

  .athlete-category-card__note {
    font-size: 0.85rem !important;
    color: #666 !important;
    font-style: italic;
    border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    padding-top: 12px;
    margin-top: auto !important;
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Athlete Categories",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Athlete Categories"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
